_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Knight</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Owl\" title=\"Owl\">Owl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rookery\" title=\"Rookery\">Rookery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sentinel\" title=\"Sentinel\">Sentinel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Skulls_of_the_Targaryen_dragons\" title=\"Skulls of the Targaryen dragons\">Skulls of the Targaryen dragons</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sparrow\" title=\"Sparrow\">Sparrow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sword_of_the_Morning\" title=\"Sword of the Morning\">Sword of the Morning</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_8&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>This page uses content from <b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://concord.fandom.com\">Concordances and Characters wiki at Fandom.com</a></b>. The original content was at <b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://concord.wikia.com/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones:_Chapter_8\">A Game of Thrones: Chapter 8</a></b>. The list of authors can be 